  "body": "I found that everytime we exec into a container, a pid file will be genernated under `/var/run/containerd/io.containerd.runtime.v1.linux/k8s.io/${CONTAINER_ID}/`.\r\n\r\nIt seems that we don't clean it up after exec is deleted:\r\n```\r\n/var/run/containerd/io.containerd.runtime.v1.linux/k8s.io/883224866fb7820da31a2e16656e159a2b1d672aa86a6079a5cfcad2fbc25144/init.pid\r\n/var/run/containerd/io.containerd.runtime.v1.linux/k8s.io/7e437e86b6c2f9fcbbc30809725477ac68f8ee057e46910de73a5a9bed7d99ab/7912cdd8a2ac8ec1ee624e91e16b2f67e83da9b21922c6ba1e3e07933af15720.pid\r\n/var/run/containerd/io.containerd.runtime.v1.linux/k8s.io/7e437e86b6c2f9fcbbc30809725477ac68f8ee057e46910de73a5a9bed7d99ab/79a1354c5ce3d8df87f687e933171e8cfea47a6b9eaa55c6bac0e4743515ef8e.pid\r\n/var/run/containerd/io.containerd.runtime.v1.linux/k8s.io/7e437e86b6c2f9fcbbc30809725477ac68f8ee057e46910de73a5a9bed7d99ab/7e75387cc7ef2959527474ed1fb78fad63ba256ff9a45ef7dd81093b291d3dba.pid\r\n/var/run/containerd/io.containerd.runtime.v1.linux/k8s.io/7e437e86b6c2f9fcbbc30809725477ac68f8ee057e46910de73a5a9bed7d99ab/3c92ec291c903e2b9c16bff4f05653c92f69c103f811d90f9bb548e26879e136.pid\r\n/var/run/containerd/io.containerd.runtime.v1.linux/k8s.io/7e437e86b6c2f9fcbbc30809725477ac68f8ee057e46910de73a5a9bed7d99ab/5f65bf927c852acc99afe09087cc17a51a8934cd0203c3de3a547d61fa6a820b.pid\r\n/var/run/containerd/io.containerd.runtime.v1.linux/k8s.io/7e437e86b6c2f9fcbbc30809725477ac68f8ee057e46910de73a5a9bed7d99ab/a379e1fa6ef9f6032d1db47a440260b003b2b0456ba3f9f5b34118e516c67ae7.pid\r\n/var/run/containerd/io.containerd.runtime.v1.linux/k8s.io/7e437e86b6c2f9fcbbc30809725477ac68f8ee057e46910de73a5a9bed7d99ab/1dd76206d7a1f1bbf04a145ed0f0cc3a02954dd3acb55a70da987f5efb699196.pid\r\n/var/run/containerd/io.containerd.runtime.v1.linux/k8s.io/7e437e86b6c2f9fcbbc30809725477ac68f8ee057e46910de73a5a9bed7d99ab/714eaff3bdd9e78c8bf3d164009ef13211b696b2912258c16ec37911d491d037.pid\r\n```\r\n\r\nIs this expected behavior?",
